Boipelo Mere The launch of the Robert Mangaliso Sobukwe exhibition took place at the McGregor Museum in Kimberley on Thursday (10/05). It was hosted by the McGregor Museum Trustees, the Northern Cape Department of Sports, Arts and Culture and the Sol Plaatje University. Retired Judge Bernard Ngoepe delivered the lecture on Sobikwe. 24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.  